      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "738722",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "WEJILA369369",
        "uid": "127079"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t主要是饮用水，现在自来水都不能放心的喝，地下水污染严重，要想控制全国百姓自来水投毒最简单\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-04-06",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "785838",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "肥皂制造家",
        "uid": "121272"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t地里的根茎相对干净，因为种在地里，农药杀虫剂比较难作用到。而且这些低密度作物，大量施化肥不值当。<br/>\n<br/>\n这是我当一辈子农民的姥爷说的。所多吃土豆，地瓜，山药，芋头就对了。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-11-23",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "785839",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "PUA雾里看花",
        "uid": "138344"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t进口的猫狗粮绝对是安全健康多吃不胖。我的话打算多屯集一些发国难财。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2024-11-23",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
